Map Name: cs_glass-attack

Creator: TK|Kev

Player Size: 12v12

Date Made: July 13th 2011

Description
-------------------------------

This is a remake from the popular Call of Duty United Offensive version,
I have added my own little bits in to the map, this map is a good size for 12v12 match
and could probaly hold more. Time estimated of construction was about 2/3 hours with 
help from my friend TK|Tez. enjoy and have fun. :D
